htds

Class AlertLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • htds.AlertLog

  • public class AlertLog
extends java.lang.Object
    The AlertLog class is a data member in the Alert class to keep logging information about an Alert object It records information about 1- Who created the alert (i.e. the user who performed the analysis) 2- when (Date/Time) the alert was created (i.e. populated to the database) 3- Which data tuples in the database were analyzed to generate the Alert 4- The AlertProfile used to generate the alert Once an AlertLog object is created, it can not be modified
    Author:
    Qutaiba
